Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is the turbulent Sengoku period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:11.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Warlords keep on fighting day and night over\NJipangu State, where Karakuri people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:16.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri martial artists were sharpening their swords, dreaming of victory and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:23.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,And now, a wild hero has arrived, seeking to be the number one Karakuri martial artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:33.22,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\an8\fs32\fade(770,0)}Karakuri Kengouden
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:33.22,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\fade(770,0)}Musashi Road
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:33.22,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\fs24\fade(770,0)}(The Story of {\i1}Karakuri{\i0} Martial Artist: Road of Musashi)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:38.06,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,A man always dreams of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:41.81,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,in the center of the world to become
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:44.69,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,AH! AH! the strongest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:49.74,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Raise the sword of your heart high to the wide sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:54.37,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Raise the curtain to the road of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:01:00.96,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,A skilled swordsman roams on Jipangu State
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:06.59,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His name is Musashi, a Karakuri man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:08.09,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Go! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:11.01,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,The sound of fierce duels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:13.84,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,makes life dazzling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:19.31,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Battles of yesterdays make you stronger today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:25.56,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:28.48,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will be glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.03,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,The sound of fierce duels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:33.53,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,makes life dazzling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:39.62,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Fight the utmost with the stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:45.88,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:51.13,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His eyes shined! Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:06.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dreaming for the number one martial artist of Jipangu State, Musashi was fighting against numberless Martial Artists,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:14.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,but he met a wrong opponent, the infamous Denshichirō, the boss of Yoshika Dōjō
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,boasting countless members across the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.16,TitleEP,en,0,0,200,,Kotetsu the Excellent Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.16,TitleEP,en,0,0,60,,Calls for a Storm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:35.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's very absurd, to have a match with that wooden sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:40.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,A match between martial artists shall only be done with real swords like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:55.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,I lost! I'm going to die-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Someone help me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:00.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kid, you're half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,It was a persimmon-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:10.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,We were going under a persimmon tree moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:15.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't know what were you dreaming about, but you were pretty agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn, I want a sword too-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:25.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will get a sword and become the number one martial artist of Jipangu-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,We're soon at Sakai village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.72,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\move(300,280,300,-20)\frx20\t(0,3100,\fs48)\fs40}Welcome to Sakai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:35.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,This place is Sakai harbor, a village of merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:43.61,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs105\q2\frz-88\frx2\fax-0.1\move(345,134,345,-500)}Yoshioka Dōjō Inc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.61,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs80\frz-88\frx2\fax-0.1\move(263,471,263,-63)}Sakai Branch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:41.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Denshichiro came to Yoshioka Dōjō Sakai branch to get Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:47.64,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs46\frz-82.5\frx2\fax-0.1\t(0,4000,\fs58)\move(520,-1,660,-73)}Yoshioka Dōjō Inc.
