Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:47.64,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs24\t(0,4000,\fs30)\frx20\frz2.5\pos(314,266)}Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:52.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is the face of Musashi who wreaked havoc on our Yoshioka Dōjō.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a sly face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:01.34,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs26\move(334,115,340,95)\t(0,4670,\fs30)}Martial Arts is about Form
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:59.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,He should be in this Sakai village. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:05.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Search for him thoroughly and report to me as soon as you find out where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:08.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,He is not just a weak brat, so be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:13.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:14.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,The sword craftsman you asked for is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good. I'll go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:32.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,This person, Kenmochi Kotetsu, is a historically famous sword craftsman of the long Sengoku period of Jipangu State.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.42,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz26\fs32\fad(0,300)\pos(337,242)\c&H8989FF&}Made by Kotetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:40.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,A sword crafted by him is called Kotetsu, and it is told that only masters of swords can have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:51.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Denshichirō Yoshioka, a substitute instructor at Yoshioka Dōjō.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kenmochi Kotetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Long story short, I'd like to ask you to make your excellent sword Kotetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,I reject.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:05.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! You dare to reject the request from the substitute instructor at Yoshioka Dōjō?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:14.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't you know Yoshioka Denshichirō, a name famous all over Jipangu State?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,I do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:22.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then why do you reject? Crafting a sword isn't something dishonorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,I regret to say that I already gave up crafting swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,How's this? We'll pay as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,I do not want money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see that you are without greed. But know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:46.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Whatever reason you have, you will make and give me a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait! He is not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will allow you ten days!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will go receive it myself. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you alright with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:07.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,No matter how wide Jipangu is, nobody dared to deny my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:13.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Moreover, I can't count how many people lost their lives by denying my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:24.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am starved to death-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,This smell must be dango-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.18,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an4\frz-90\move(177,188,177,188)}Dango 5 mon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.18,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an4\move(120,189,120,189)\frz-93}Tea 1 mon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,My belly's going to meet my back-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
